### Enrichment
No formal PKM interoperability standard exists in the broader ecosystem as of 2026 — BKS is a novel contribution. The AI4PKM project (Seattle, 2025) combines AI and PKM but lacks a formal interchange spec. Obsidian community preference for open Markdown formats validates the BKS Markdown-first approach. Consider publishing BKS as a public specification.

